*purge*.md
*PURGE*.md
*history*.md
*HISTORY*.md
*remediation*.md
*REMEDIATION*.md
SECURITY_REMEDIATION*.md
REPOSITORY_STATUS*.md
SECURITY_IMPLEMENTATION*.md
SECURITY_AUDIT*.md

