# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/cuda_cache/**
**/.nv/**
**/*.cubin
**/*.ptx

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Keep These (Negation Patterns)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
!README.md
!DISCLAIMER.md
!LICENSE
!LICENSE-MIT
!LICENSE-AGPL
!ARCHITECTURE.md
!INSTALL.md
!USAGE.md
!TODO.md
!AGENTS.md
